<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Community Project</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background: #1f2937;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #60a5fa;
        }

        .hero {
            background: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        section {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            background: #1f2937;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: white;
            color: #2563eb;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background: #e5e7eb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Community Project</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="#goal">Our Goal</a>
            <a href="#help">How You Can Help</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Making a Difference Together</h1>
        <p>Join us in creating positive change in our community.</p>
        <a href="#help" class="button">Get Involved</a>
    </section>

    <section id="goal">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Our Goal</h2>
            <p>
                Our mission is to bring people together to support meaningful
                projects, share resources, and create opportunities that improve
                lives. We believe that small actions can lead to big results when
                a community works together.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="help">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>How You Can Help</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Volunteer your time and skills.</li>
                <li>Share our mission with friends and family.</li>
                <li>Participate in community events.</li>
                <li>Contribute ideas and feedback.</li>
                <li>Support ongoing projects and initiatives.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>Email: contact@example.com</p>
            <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>
            <p>Location: Your City, State</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Community Project. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
